================================================================================

We acknowledge and thank the original authors and contributors of ginx for their
excellent work, which served as the foundation for this project.

Key components derived from ginx:
- Core handler wrapper pattern (W/B/S/BS)
- Session management architecture
- Middleware framework
- Context enhancement concepts

All modifications and new features in gint are also licensed under Apache License 2.0.

